---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About | Tsatsin Blog"
  description="About this blog and what gets published here."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
    <h1>Notes from shipping</h1>
    <p>
      I use this blog to share practical lessons from building software and launching projects.
      Everything here is written to be useful in under five minutes.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="about-grid" aria-label="What this blog covers">
    <article class="about-panel">
      <h2>What I write about</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Architecture choices and trade-offs.</li>
        <li>Simple systems that are easy to maintain.</li>
        <li>Shipping notes from real projects.</li>
      </ul>
    </article>

    <article class="about-panel">
      <h2>How I write</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>One idea per post.</li>
        <li>Examples over theory.</li>
        <li>Clear language, no fluff.</li>
      </ul>
    </article>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
